@startuml
title ATM - Withdrawal Process

[*] --> WaitingForCard

state WaitingForCard
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state ProvidingOptions
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state DispensingCash
state PrintingReceipt
state ReturningCard
state TerminatingTransaction

WaitingForCard --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN

ValidatingPIN --> ProvidingOptions : Valid PIN / Display Menu

ProvidingOptions --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected / Request Withdrawal

ProcessingWithdrawal --> DispensingCash : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash

DispensingCash --> PrintingReceipt : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt

PrintingReceipt --> ReturningCard : Receipt Printed / Eject

ReturningCard --> TerminatingTransaction : Card Returned / Reset

TerminatingTransaction --> WaitingForCard : After (Elapsed Time) / Reset System
@enduml
